1. taloloda ki taiyaiya ni mobeleng si athingala si animiyanga si akakeceng ki kakoza ai tara alolodo lani macocongolo kai taiyaiya, alolodo dwakale ki taiyaiya lalra dwakalenga. savagavaga si katha, kai acocongola si tokocingalre ki taiyaiya arakai ki vaga, ’acase si sa’atothingala; 
[===]
la kaiyasa kai drare’e kai vaga ki sa’arairaisa, amalranga ’aelrelre si aibibonga, akabalrithi si kiyarakenga ki sa’arairaisa. arakai ki sa’elaela, arakai ki mathariringa akakeceng si lrigila, tarakiso’ilri kaiyasasa ka omase si sininadromana aiyaiya, athingalenga la akakeceng kidremedreme ki tacekecekela, aro mwadringi kai acoga ki sininadromana ka taiyaiya si aro tobaowa.
